column10:
Counter-Strike: Source itself is fine, but its the server aspect that makes this review a thumbs down.
Here is a list of problems with CS:S servers
[olist]
[*]Revive mechanics;
[*]Fake player counts;
[*]Fake servers that pose as advertisements;
[*]Pay-to-win benefits such as extra health, money;
[*]Some servers will display your IP address in the chat.
[/olist]
I do not recommend buying this, unless you are going to play with bots or on a LAN.
